values: I got a condo with some friends. and went to the club. I didnt expect what Happened. Gun shots went off. total crazy in that club. People running and pushing to the doors. People trashing the place and breaking tables. Krystal- I'm glad I called you even if it was only for 5 seconds. Why cant we just have any fun anymore?
